Mouse 0 2 A Close
Mouse 0 4 A Maximize
Mouse 0 6 A Thumbnail
Mouse 1 I A DeThumbnail
Mouse 1 I A DeThumbnail
Mouse 1 R A Menu MenuFvwmRoot Nop
Mouse 1 T A FuncMoveOrMaximize
Mouse 1 T A FuncMoveOrMaximize
Mouse 1 W M FuncMoveOrMaximize
Mouse 1 W M FuncMoveOrMaximize
Mouse 3 R A WindowList NoGeometry
Mouse 3 R A WindowList NoGeometry



